trans-unit.source:
\n

Enumerates the text elements of a string.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxx xxxxxxxx xx x xxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

Gets the current text element in the string.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An object containing the current text element in the string.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

The enumerator is positioned before the first text element of the string or after the last text element.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxx xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx xx xxxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

Gets the index of the text element that the enumerator is currently positioned over.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

The index of the text element that the enumerator is currently positioned over.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

The enumerator is positioned before the first text element of the string or after the last text element.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxx xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx xx xxxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

Gets the current text element in the string.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

A new string containing the current text element in the string being read.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxx xxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx xxxxx xxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

The enumerator is positioned before the first text element of the string or after the last text element.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxx xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx xx xxxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

Advances the enumerator to the next text element of the string.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xx xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source: true if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next text element; false if the enumerator has passed the end of the string.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$$x$xxxxxx$xxxx$$xxxxxx$ xx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxx$ $xxxxxx$xxxxx$$xxxxxx$ xx xxx xxxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxx xxx xxx xx xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first text element in the string.

\n
